        public boolean isJoinable(int leaveEmptySeats)
        Checks if this table is joinable. A table is considered joinable if it the number of empty seats is larger than leaveEmptySeats. For example, if leaveEmptySeats = 2, a table is joinable if it has 3 or more empty seats.
